It goes completely on in the imaginated happening, everything is real, even later in memory.
These inner journeys are fundamentally different for Claussen from any dream.
Dream is another state, he describes his experience.
In contrast, the memories from mental travels are still clear to me after years and in side-by-side details.
More clearly and intensely than actually experienced.
